<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV78">
<l>naliyu narakaṉai vīṭṭiṟṟum vāṇaṉtiṇ ṭōḷtuṇitta</l>
<l>valiyum perumaiyum yāñcollun nīrttalla maivaraipōl</l>
<l>poliyu muruviṟ pirāṉār puṉaipūn tuḻāymalarkkē</l>
<l>meliyu maṭaneñci ṉārtantu pōyiṉa vētaṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They are not of the nature we speak of as killing the distressful hell resident,</l>
<l>the strength and greatness that cut off the firm arms of Bhāṇa – the agonies</l>
<l>brought on those with foolish hearts that soften for the Tulsi blossoms,</l>
<l>flowers adorning the lord with a flourishing form like a cloudy mountain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
